DEFINE BAR 8 OF recepciónt PROMPT "\-"
DEFINE BAR 9 OF recepciónt PROMPT "Monitor de Trazabilidad"
ON SELECTION BAR 1 OF recepciónt do form frmfarmacia34
ON SELECTION BAR 2 OF recepciónt do form frmfarmacia36
ON SELECTION BAR 3 OF recepciónt do form frmfarmacia37
ON SELECTION BAR 4 OF recepciónt do form frmfarmacia38
ON SELECTION BAR 5 OF recepciónt do form frmfarmacia40
ON SELECTION BAR 6 OF recepciónt do form frmfarmacia42 with "L"
